									<div class="news_newspost"><a href="/riders-of-icarus/developer-journals/more-about-mounts-1000011254"><img src="http://images.mmorpg.com/images/heroes/features/11254.jpg" width="466" border="0" alt="More About Mounts - Riders of Icarus Developer Journals" style="padding-bottom:5px;" /></a><p>Greetings, Riders! It's BK again, the lead game designer for the Riders of Icarus development team at WeMade. Collecting mounts is a core feature of Riders of Icarus, and in this DEV Blog I'll discuss my two favorite mounts and some of the decisions we've made while designing mounts in the game.  </p></div>
									<div class="posted">Posted Oct 19, 2016 by Suzie Ford</div>
									<div class="forum">
										<div class="fimfo">
										<a href="/riders-of-icarus" title="Riders of Icarus Game Info">Riders of Icarus</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="/riders-of-icarus/developer-journals" title="Riders of Icarus Developer Journals">Developer Journals</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="/riders-of-icarus/developer-journals/more-about-mounts-1000011254" vanilla-identifier="news_41785">Comments</a>
										</div>
