									</div>
									<div class="clear"></div>

								</div>





								<div class="newsitem">
									<h3 class="title"><a href="/news/funcoms-hide-and-shriek-to-be-released-on-october-25th-1000041782">Funcom's Hide & Shriek to be Released on October 25th</a></h3>

									<div class="news_newspost"><a href="/news/funcoms-hide-and-shriek-to-be-released-on-october-25th-1000041782"><img src="http://images.mmorpg.com/images/heroes/news/41782.jpg" width="466" border="0" alt="Funcom's Hide &amp; Shriek to be Released on October 25th" style="padding-bottom:5px;" /></a><p>Funcom has announced that its fright-fest title, Hide & Shriek, will be released on Tuesday, October 25th. Hide & Shriek is a game where the objective is to literally (and virtually) scare an opponent to death.</p></div>
									<div class="posted">Posted Oct 19, 2016 by Suzie Ford</div>
									<div class="forum">
										<div class="fimfo">
										General&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="/news" title=" News">News</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="/news/funcoms-hide-and-shriek-to-be-released-on-october-25th-1000041782" vanilla-identifier="news_41782">Comments</a>
